Information
------------------------------
Over 100,000 Chinese millionaires have moved to Vancouver, sparking everything from a reality show to a property boom making housing unaffordable.$151,000 for a diamond necklace? $140,000 for a piano? $15,000 for a handbag?
This is everyday life for the Ultra Rich Asian Girls of Vancouver, played out in front of millions on reality TV. Dateline asks if the millionaire migrants are a blessing or curse.
